description:
Hey everyone! I thought it would fun to do a short series on this game I've been playing recently, The Pit. 

This is a space themed rogue-like game where you go through randomly generated floors, encounter random enemies, acquire random items, and do your best to build your character up so he can survive to the end. Every run of the game can take several hours and can be very different from each other depending on what you get and the choices you make.

http://store.steampowered.com/app/233700/
